=== assistant text ===
The Raman spectrum from `graphene.dat` was processed by parsing the coordinate pairs, identifying the G peak region (~1400-1700 cm⁻¹) and the 2D peak region (~2600-2900 cm⁻¹), and fitting each with a Lorentzian function using `scipy.optimize.curve_fit`. The resulting parameters (x0, gamma, amplitude, and offset) were saved to `/app/results.json`.

